reviewText: I am giving you some info on the other shows on this tape. In "Baseball Tommy", Stu and Grandpa take Tommy to a baseball game. Tommy lets go of his balloon and wanders around the stadium to find it.  Will Stu and Grandpa find Tommy? In "Rebel Without a Teddy Bear"  (which should be called "Rebel Without a Lion"), Didi throws  Henry, Tommy's stuffed lion away. Angelica tells Tommy that if he acts like  a rotten brat, he'll get Henry back. Will he? in "Case of the Missing  Rugrat", Tommy gets driven to a palace. Will Grandpa Lou find Tommy at  the palace that he's at? Well, that's all the shows. Enjoy!
Daughter loves this....only a 20 minute tape, but she likes her "old tapes"
Arrived earlier than expected, and was just as described.
